        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs. 1-6. Kathroperla perdita eggs. 1-4. Ross Creek, Lincoln Co., Montana. 5-6. Grande Ronde River, Union Co., Oregon. 1. Egg, lateral. 2. Chorionic detail (lt = linear tubercle; m = micropyle). 3. Collar end of egg (a = anchor). 4. Anterior pole (lid) of egg. 5. Collar end of egg (s = stria). 6. Anterior pole of egg." ;
